  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/coretext\/ctlinebreakmode\ncrawled: 2025-12-14T15:21:23Z\n---\n\n# CTLineBreakMode\n\n**Enumeration**\n\nThese constants specify what happens when a line is too long for its frame.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nenum CTLineBreakMode\n```\n\n## Constants\n\n- **CTLineBreakMode.byWordWrapping**\n- **CTLineBreakMode.byCharWrapping**\n- **CTLineBreakMode.byClipping**\n- **CTLineBreakMode.byTruncatingHead**\n- **CTLineBreakMode.byTruncatingTail**\n- **CTLineBreakMode.byTruncatingMiddle**\n\n## Initializers\n\n- **init(rawValue:)**\n\n## Constants\n\n- **CTTextAlignment**: Constants that specify text alignment.\n- **CTWritingDirection**: These constants specify the writing direction.\n- **CTParagraphStyleSpecifier**: Constants used to query and modify a paragraph style object.\n\n## Conforms To\n\n- BitwiseCopyable\n- Equatable\n- Hashable\n- RawRepresentable\n- Sendable\n- SendableMetatype\n\n",
